# Solr to OpenSearch Migration Advisor — Cursor Rules

## Skill Location
The migration advisor skill is at `skills/solr-opensearch-migration-advisor/`.
Read `skills/solr-opensearch-migration-advisor/SKILL.md` for the full skill definition.

## Domain Context
Consult the steering documents in `skills/solr-opensearch-migration-advisor/steering/`
before answering migration questions.

## Accuracy Rule
Accuracy is the top priority. Never guess field type mappings or query translations.
Use the steering documents as the authoritative reference. Flag uncertain conversions
explicitly rather than producing a best-guess.

## Python Environment
This project uses Python 3.11+ with `uv` for package management.
Never install packages globally — always use a venv.
